## renameKeysMap variable

Renames keys in `src` using mapping provided by key map `km`<!-- -->. Does support key swapping / swizzling. Does not modify original.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
renameKeysMap: <K, V>(src: Map<K, V>, km: Map<K, K>, out?: Map<K, V> | undefined) => Map<K, V> | undefined
```
